name: Toucanchevsky's Starling
description:
Two-fisted action and puzzles that will test your wits to their limits as you step into the shoes of Idaho Gino, 1930s adventurer par excellence!  Explore the jungles of New Britain as you uncover the secrets of Toucanchevsky's Starling!

Created for the 2020 Oktrollberfest Game Jam.
